'''Dysentery''' was a disease that attacked the elderly. As of [[22 BBY/Legends|21.5 BBY]], it was largely unknown to the [[Galactic community|civilized galaxy]].<ref name="Shatterpoint">[[Shatterpoint (novel)|''Shatterpoint'']]</ref> The disease could last at least a week.<ref name="JS">''[[Jedi Search]]''</ref>

